        {
          "id": "c02-p02",
          "chapter": "流畅回答为什么不等于事实",
          "chapterNumber": 2,
          "paragraphNumber": 2,
          "narration": "语言模型产生答案时，并不是从一个写着“今天天气”的抽屉里取出事实。它更像是在判断：根据眼前这些文字，下一句怎样说最合理。这也解释了什么叫幻觉。幻觉不是语句奇怪，也不只是偶尔口误，而是模型用非常合理的表达，给出了一个可以核对、但实际错误的事实。",
          "headline": "幻觉：说得合理，不代表事实正确",
          "coreLabel": "下一句合理 ≠ 当前事实成立",
          "type": "mechanism",
          "layout": "human-agent-prop",
          "generatedArt": null,
          "temporaryGenerated": false,
          "generatedArtSide": null,
          "highlightSide": null,
          "motionType": "nudge",
          "recapPoints": null,
          "human": "explain-front",
          "humanDirection": "front",
          "agent": "reason-front",
          "agentDirection": "front",
          "props": [
            {
              "id": "warning"
            }
          ],
          "renderHuman": true,
          "renderAgent": true,
          "coreObjectCount": 1,
          "start": 56.387,
          "end": 78.485
        },
        {
          "id": "c02-p03",
          "chapter": "流畅回答为什么不等于事实",
          "chapterNumber": 2,
          "paragraphNumber": 3,
          "narration": "模型在预训练中学到的，主要是文字和事实通常怎样一起出现。它不会在读到每句话时，都同时得到一张可靠的真假标签。像“水在零摄氏度附近结冰”这种高频而稳定的知识，语言里有大量重复线索。可是“你家附近今天下午四点会不会下雨”，既具体又随时变化，无法靠过去的语言规律补回当前真相。",
          "headline": "语言规律补不回今天下午的天气",
          "coreLabel": "历史文字没有当前观察",
          "type": "case",
          "layout": "generated",
          "generatedArt": "guess-vs-unknown.png",
          "temporaryGenerated": true,
          "generatedArtSide": "right",
          "highlightSide": "left",
          "motionType": "sine-float",
          "recapPoints": null,
          "human": "idle",
          "humanDirection": "front",
          "agent": "read-front",
          "agentDirection": "front",
          "props": [
            {
              "id": "document-stack"
            }
          ],
          "renderHuman": false,
          "renderAgent": false,
          "coreObjectCount": 1,
          "start": 78.485,
          "end": 103.08
        },
        {
          "id": "c02-p04",
          "chapter": "流畅回答为什么不等于事实",
          "chapterNumber": 2,
          "paragraphNumber": 4,
          "narration": "所以模型能够把一句话说得很像答案，不代表它已经观察到了答案所依赖的事实。生成能力和事实获取能力，是两件不同的事。",
          "headline": "生成能力和事实获取能力是两件事",
          "coreLabel": "会表达 ≠ 已经观察事实",
          "type": "mechanism",
          "layout": "two-props",
          "generatedArt": null,
          "temporaryGenerated": false,
          "generatedArtSide": null,
          "highlightSide": null,
          "motionType": "spring-pop",
          "recapPoints": null,
          "human": "idle",
          "humanDirection": "front",
          "agent": "reason-front",
